comment: Barea (DAL) maintains legal guarding position and does not affect Teague's (IND) movement to the basket.
LHH shows Ellis (IND) establishes position and makes incidental contact with Barnes (DAL) on the rebound.
Matthews (DAL) makes contact to the body of Ellis (IND) and affects his SQBR. Contact occurs before the gather.
Young (IND) makes contact to the body of Barnes (DAL) and affects his FOM.
Teague (IND) makes incidental contact with Barea (DAL) and does not affect his FOM.
Turner (IND) makes incidental contact with Barnes (DAL) and does not impede him from contesting the drive.
Nowitzki (DAL) hand checks Ellis (IND) without affecting his SQBR.
RATR shows Barea (DAL) makes marginal contact with Young (IND), who trips while back peddling.
Matthews (DAL) commits a take foul on Teague (IND).
Matthews (DAL) makes incidental contact with George (IND) on the inbound.
George (IND) sets the screen on Barnes (DAL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that George's (IND) put back shot occured after the buzzer was upheld.
Turner (IND) delivers contact to Williams (DAL) as he sets his screen.
RHH shows George (IND) makes marginal contact with Nowitzki (DAL) using his off arm that does not dislodge Nowitzi or affect his ability to defend.
[Observable in enhanced video] RHH shows George (IND) gathers the ball by cradling it against his body momentarily, thereby stopping his dribble before taking another step.
Ellis (IND) maintains legal guarding position on Williams (DAL) in the post and then cleanly strips the ball.
Turner (IND) establishes a legal screening position in Barnes' (DAL) path. Barnes makes marginal contact with Turner as he disengages from the screen.
Held ball by Turner (IND) and Barea (DAL).

Turner (IND) gathers the pass in the air and then lands on his left foot, takes a step with his right and releases the dribble. He then gathers the ball to end his dribble on his left foot and then takes two steps to shoot.
Anderson (DAL) commits a take foul on Ellis (IND).
Anderson (DAL) commits a take foul on Teague (IND).
[Observable in enhanced video] Brussino (DAL) moves his pivot foot.
Acy (DAL) makes contact with Teague (IND) that affects his SQBR.
